      section
        h2.bright Where?
        h3 @meteorjs
        h3
          a https://www.meteor.com/blog
        h3
          a http://thisweekinmeteor.com/
        h3
          a https://crater.io/
        h3
          a https://forums.meteor.com
        h3
          a https://github.com/meteor/meteor/blob/devel/History.md

      section
        h2.bright MDG
        h3 Meteor 1.1.0.2

      section
        h2 Full Windows Support!
        h3 Discover Meteor updated
        h3 Meteor Up updated
        h3 Velocity updated
        h3 etc...

      section
        h2 In the pipeline
        h3 Handlebars sub-expressions
        h3 Email attachments
        h3 New methods for ReactiveDict and Tracker

      section
        h2 AMA with Sashko
        h3 Mostly about packages!
        h3 Quasi-official packages
        h3 Paid packages
        h3 SSR and Lazy Loading not priorities

      section
        h2 MeteorHacks show with Justin
