        h3 ...which means "it just works":
        h3 Isolation
        h3 Scaling
        h3 Fault Tolerance
        h3 Like "meteor deploy" with a beautiful UI

      section
        h2 Interesting Packages
        h3 gwendall:template-animations
        h3 studiointeract:spiderable
        h3 peerlibrary:blaze-components
        h3 simple:rest
        h3 simple:rethink

      section
        h2 Testing
